      <body>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-1">
            <heading>Citation and commencement</heading>
            <num>1.</num>
            <content>
               <p>These Regulations may be cited as the Historical Sexual Offences (Pardons and Disregards) (Scotland) Act 2018 (Commencement) Regulations 2019 and come into force on 15 October 2019.</p>
            </content>
         </hcontainer>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-2">
